TERA XTAL Buys $30 Million Worth of Equipment From GT Solar Hong Kong

-- B y   A d e l a   L i n
-- 
2011-05-05T01:05:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/tera-xtal-buys-30-million-worth-of-equipment-from-gt-solar-hong-kong.html
TERA XTAL Technology Corp. (4969)  purchased
NT$849 million of equipment from GT Solar Hong Kong ltd. from
March 26 to May 4, the Taiwanese company said in a stock
exchange statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
